Mouse_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunCursor.png" Reloading_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunWaitCursor.png"
Tool = script.Parent
Mouse = nil
function UpdateIcon() if Mouse then Mouse.Icon = Tool.Enabled and Mouse_Icon or Reloading_Icon end end
function OnEquipped(ToolMouse) Mouse = ToolMouse UpdateIcon() end
Tool:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Enabled"):Connect(UpdateIcon) Tool.Equipped:connect(OnEquipped)

--Made by Luckymaxer
Tool = script.Parent Handle = Tool:WaitForChild("Handle") Mesh = Handle:WaitForChild("Mesh")
Buzzing = Handle:WaitForChild("Buzzing")
Players = game:GetService("Players") Debris = game:GetService("Debris")
ReloadTime = 5
Damage = 1
BeeDuration = 10 BeeSpeed = 15
Grips = { NormalGrip = CFrame.new(0.125, -0.675000012, 0.949999988, 1, 0, -3.69598024e-006, 0, 1, 0, 3.69598024e-006, 0, 1), ReleaseGrip = CFrame.new(0.125, -0.675000012, 0.949999988, 1, 0, -7.76634351e-007, 9.632965e-008, 0.992277861, 0.124034733, 7.706372e-007, -0.124034733, 0.992277861) }
Bee = Instance.new("Part") Bee.Name = "KillerBee" Bee.Material = Enum.Material.Plastic Bee.Shape = Enum.PartType.Block Bee.FormFactor = Enum.FormFactor.Custom Bee.TopSurface = Enum.SurfaceType.Smooth Bee.BottomSurface = Enum.SurfaceType.Smooth Bee.Size = Vector3.new(0.2, 0.2, 0.2) Bee.CanCollide = false BeeMesh = Instance.new("SpecialMesh") BeeMesh.MeshType = Enum.MeshType.FileMesh BeeMesh.MeshId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset?id=162005808" BeeMesh.TextureId = "http://www.roblox.com/asset?id=162005862" BeeMesh.Scale = Vector3.new(1, 1, 1) BeeMesh.Parent = Bee
function FindCharacterAncestor(Parent) if Parent and Parent ~= game:GetService("Workspace") then local humanoid = Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if humanoid then return Parent, humanoid else return FindCharacterAncestor(Parent.Parent) end end return nil end
function TagHumanoid(humanoid, player) local Creator_Tag = Instance.new("ObjectValue") Creator_Tag.Name = "creator" Creator_Tag.Value = player Debris:AddItem(Creator_Tag, 2) Creator_Tag.Parent = humanoid end
function UntagHumanoid(humanoid) for i, v in pairs(humanoid:GetChildren()) do if v:IsA("ObjectValue") and v.Name == "creator" then v:Destroy() end end end
function PositionProjectile(handle, x, y, z) local HandleClone = handle:Clone() local HandleCloneY = HandleClone:Clone() HandleCloneY.CFrame = HandleCloneY.CFrame * CFrame.Angles(math.rad(90), 0, 0) HandleCloneY.CFrame = HandleCloneY.CFrame - HandleCloneY.CFrame.lookVector * y local HandleCloneZ = HandleCloneY:Clone() HandleCloneZ.CFrame = HandleCloneZ.CFrame + HandleClone.CFrame.lookVector * z local HandleCloneX = HandleCloneZ:Clone() HandleCloneX.CFrame = HandleCloneZ.CFrame * CFrame.Angles(0, math.rad(90), 0) HandleCloneX.CFrame = HandleCloneX.CFrame - HandleCloneX.CFrame.lookVector * x return HandleCloneX.CFrame end
function CheckTable(Table, Instance) for i, v in pairs(Table) do if v == Instance then return true end end return false end
function Activated() if Tool.Enabled then Tool.Enabled = false local Positions = { Vector3.new(-0.05, 0, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), Vector3.new(-0.075, 0.2, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), Vector3.new(0.15, -0.05, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), Vector3.new(0.3, 0.1, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), Vector3.new(0.25, 0.3, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), Vector3.new(0.05, 0.35, ((Handle.Size.Z / 2) + (Bee.Size.Z / 2) - 0.15)), } local BeeModel = Instance.new("Model") BeeModel.Name = "Bees" local Bees = {} local BeeConnections = {} Spawn(function() local BeeCheck = tick() while (#Bees == 0 and (tick() - BeeCheck) < 5) do wait() end if #Bees > 0 then local BeeCheck = tick() while (#Bees > 0 and (tick() - BeeCheck) < BeeDuration) do for i, v in pairs(Bees) do if v and v.Parent then Spawn(function() local IgnoreObjects = {Character, BeeModel} local BeeRadius = 25 local NegativePartRadius = Vector3.new(((v.Size.X / 2) + (BeeRadius / 1)), 0, ((v.Size.Z / 2) + (BeeRadius / 1))) local PositivePartRadius =Vector3.new(((v.Size.X / 2) + (BeeRadius / 1)), 0, ((v.Size.Z / 2) + (BeeRadius / 1))) local Parts = game:GetService("Workspace"):FindPartsInRegion3WithIgnoreList(Region3.new(v.Position - NegativePartRadius, v.Position + PositivePartRadius), IgnoreObjects, 100) local Humanoids = {} local Torsos = {} local ClosestPlayer = {Humanoid = nil, Torso = nil, Distance = BeeRadius} for ii, vv in pairs(Parts) do if vv and vv.Parent then local humanoid = vv.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") local torso = vv.Parent:FindFirstChild("Torso") or vv.Parent:FindFirstChild("UpperTorso") if humanoid and humanoid.Health > 0 and torso and not CheckTable(Humanoids, humanoid) then table.insert(Humanoids, humanoid) table.insert(Torsos, {Humanoid = humanoid, Torso = torso}) end end end for ii, vv in pairs(Torsos) do local Distance = (vv.Torso.Position - v.Position).magnitude if vv.Humanoid.Health > 0 and Distance < ClosestPlayer.Distance then ClosestPlayer = {Humanoid = vv.Humanoid, Torso = vv.Torso, Distance = Distance} end end if v and v.Parent and ClosestPlayer.Humanoid and ClosestPlayer.Humanoid.Health > 0 and ClosestPlayer.Torso then local BeeSwarmRadius = 1 local BeeCFrame = CFrame.new(v.Position, (ClosestPlayer.Torso.Position + Vector3.new(math.random(-BeeSwarmRadius, BeeSwarmRadius), math.random(-BeeSwarmRadius, BeeSwarmRadius), math.random(-BeeSwarmRadius, BeeSwarmRadius)))) * CFrame.Angles(0, math.pi, 0) v.BodyGyro.cframe = BeeCFrame v.Velocity = BeeCFrame.lookVector * -BeeSpeed end end) end end wait() end end for i, v in pairs(BeeConnections) do v:disconnect() end BeeModel:Destroy() end) Debris:AddItem(BeeModel, BeeDuration) BeeModel.Parent = game:GetService("Workspace") for i = 1, 5 do if not Equipped then break end local OriginalCFrame = Handle.CFrame Tool.Grip = Grips.ReleaseGrip for ii, vv in pairs(Positions) do local BeeClone = Bee:Clone() local BodyForce = Instance.new("BodyForce") BodyForce.force = Vector3.new(0, BeeClone:GetMass() * 196.20, 0) BodyForce.Parent = BeeClone local BeeCFrame = PositionProjectile(Handle, vv.X, vv.Y, vv.Z) * CFrame.Angles(math.pi + math.rad(30), (-math.pi + math.rad(30)), math.rad(45)) local BodyGyro = Instance.new("BodyGyro") BodyGyro.maxTorque = Vector3.new(1e+5, 1e+5, 1e+5) BodyGyro.cframe = BeeCFrame BodyGyro.Parent = BeeClone BeeClone.Touched:connect(function(Hit) if Hit and Hit.Parent and Hit.Parent ~= Character then local humanoid = Hit.Parent:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if humanoid and humanoid.Health > 0 then UntagHumanoid(humanoid) TagHumanoid(humanoid, Player) humanoid:TakeDamage(Damage) end end end)
local BeeRemoved = BeeClone:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Parent"):Connect(function() if BeeClone.Parent == nil then for iii, vvv in pairs(Bees) do if vvv == BeeClone then table.remove(Bees, iii) end end end end) table.insert(BeeConnections, BeeRemoved) table.insert(Bees, BeeClone) BeeClone.Parent = BeeModel BeeClone.CFrame = BeeCFrame BeeClone.Velocity = CFrame.new(BeeClone.Position, Vector3.new(OriginalCFrame.p.X, BeeClone.Position.Y, OriginalCFrame.p.Z)).lookVector * -BeeSpeed end wait(0.25) Tool.Grip = Grips.NormalGrip wait(0.25) end while BeeModel and BeeModel.Parent do wait() end wait(ReloadTime) Tool.Enabled = true end end
function Equipped(Mouse) Character = Tool.Parent Player = Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(Character) Humanoid = Character:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") Torso = Character:FindFirstChild("Torso") or Character:FindFirstChild("UpperTorso") if not Character or not Humanoid or not Torso then return end Equipped = true Tool.Grip = Grips.NormalGrip if not Tool.Enabled then wait(ReloadTime) Tool.Enabled = true end end
function Unequipped() Equipped = false end
Tool.Activated:connect(Activated) Tool.Equipped:connect(Equipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(Unequipped)
